332
00:30:10,370 --> 00:30:13,860
Your Majesty, please spare me.
If I go in, I won't be able to get back out.

333
00:30:13,860 --> 00:30:16,870
- Stop your nonsense. Quickly go in! Go in!
- Your Majesty!

334
00:30:16,870 --> 00:30:19,090
