335
00:30:19,090 --> 00:30:21,530
Your Majesty, calm down...
With only him going in, it won't solve the problem.

336
00:30:21,530 --> 00:30:23,510
Those students have already been trained
in their respective schools.

337
00:30:23,510 --> 00:30:26,360
Each one has exceptional abilities.
They surely can turn this misfortune into a good one.

338
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:29,990
