None of you can get out.

344
00:33:01,900 --> 00:33:03,920
I also forgot to tell you

345
00:33:04,630 --> 00:33:06,860
that during the competition,

346
00:33:06,860 --> 00:33:11,010
the poison you took in, not only has the Beast Flame,

347
00:33:11,600 --> 00:33:13,720
