349
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:24,110
Now, it's time for you to bid us farewell.

350
00:34:04,840 --> 00:34:07,760
- We can go out now!
- Yes, there's now hope!

351
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:09,800
