356
00:34:46,699 --> 00:34:48,109
Hurry!

357
00:34:49,510 --> 00:34:52,760
Quickly go! Hurry! Run!

358
00:34:52,760 --> 00:34:55,130
Hurry! Hurry!

359
00:34:55,130 --> 00:34:56,840
Xiao Yan, let me help you!

360
00:34:56,840 --> 00:34:58,530
