361
00:34:58,530 --> 00:34:59,760
I'm not leaving!

362
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:01,199
Hurry! Be obedient!

363
00:35:01,199 --> 00:35:04,589
Once you get out, I will immediately follow.
All right?! Quickly go!

364
00:35:04,590 --> 00:35:07,400
- I told you already that I'm not going!
- There's no more time!

365
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:09,120
